{"tid":2196841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧籲東盟採取行動回應中國南海霸凌行為 越南表示歡迎美國協助","createTime":"2020-09-10T07:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T09:18:46.000Z","uid":60545,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e1ac88dc9fd46cba3805b4c7d009e81cc81470","tid":2196841,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧要求東南亞國家, 要採取行動, 回應中國在南海的霸凌行為, 承諾美國會全力支持, 美國國務院發言人說, 蓬佩奧呼籲東盟和平解決南海爭議.<br />\n        蓬佩奧透過視像和東盟外長會面, 呼籲東盟十個成員國要採取行動, 不可以被中國共產黨踐踏, 要有信心, 美國會全力協助, 他批評中國無尊重東盟約章中列明的民主價值, 主權原則和領土完整.<br />\n<br />\n        越南外長范平明說, 歡迎美國為維持區內和平, 穩定和安全, 作出貢獻, 東盟和美國是互惠的關係. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200910145925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200910145925&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=bcc3d045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200910145925</a>"},{"pid":"5c90b3e9dd90a6793070bb3128af7c9df6d248eb","tid":2196841,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"大把廠搬緊嚟東南亞, 仲使撚睇支那面色?!"},{"pid":"6c66161f5938b3c0bd5a0507252b9b6151428cb1","tid":2196841,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"東盟出黎啦，美國撐你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a134669ccb8b9b6499a0ddb5c66d56eada96939","tid":2196841,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"No military actions?"},{"pid":"d7b27cf2dc185ca9c6ef8062123293b4e03885be","tid":2196841,"uid":281437,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T07:58:55.000Z","msg":"救快必<br />\n要向法庭提供真實証據<br />\n寫「是特首的言行令我憎惡政府」在紙或布上<br />\n日日貼在手袋，背包上，帶出街